cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as it focuses on the calibration of RGB-D cameras for robotics applications. Computer Vision (cs.CV) is also a likely sub-category as the paper deals with image processing and object recognition. Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) are possible sub-categories as the paper proposes a novel error model for calibration. Graphics (cs.GR) is also a possible sub-category as the paper deals with 3D environment reconstruction and mapping.
